Class Description
Bucket

Collection
Models a Collection in a Mongo database by keeping track of specific properties of a collections.
Column
Resembles an SQL column and contains column info.

Establishes a connection with a Couchbase bucket based on the password, username, host, and bucket name provided.
Database
The model for the functions that all database representations should contain.
DatabaseDifferenceCheckerException
Used to wrap exception that occur throughtout the program.
DbConn
Establishes a connection with a database and runs the necessary statements to get schema information.
DBDiffCheckerGUI
A JFrame that has several tabs and includes the entire frontend.
FileHandler
Deals with all data coming from and going out to files.
Index
Resembles a generic index and contains index info.
MongoConn
Establishes a connection with a Mongo database based on the password, username, host, port, and database name provided.
MongoDB
Models a Mongo Database by keeping track of all collections.
MySQLConn
Establishes a connection with a MySQL database based on the password, username, port, host, and database provided.
MySQLTable

Schema
Holds common methods and instance variables for Schema subclasses.
SQLDatabase
Models an SQL database schema.
SQLDbConn
Establishes a connection with an SQL database and runs the necessary SQL statements to get schema information.

Establishes a connection with an SQL database based on the path to the database and database name.
SQLiteTable
Resembles a table in SQLite and contains info about the table's columns and indices.
StopWatch

Table
Resembles a table in an SQL database and contains info about the table's columns and indices.
View
Resembles a view in an SQL database and contains view info.
